@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ofarod(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((v1 / v1) - ((v2 + 0.00 + tmp + 0.39) + (v2 + 0.61 + tmp + 0.78)))
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.79 + v1 + 0.01)) * wp.abs(v2))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = (v0 + wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.55)))
    v1 = (0.59 - ((v2 + 0.86 + v1 + 0.05) * wp.abs(v2 + 0.45)))
    data[tid] = v0
